# Won’t that be grand?

Watching Tron (happy 44th birthday!).

The following exchange, about 15m in, felt relevant to today.

Walter: “Gotta expect some static. After all, computers are just machines. They can't think.”
Alan: “Some programs'll be thinking soon.”
Walter: (Chuckles) “Won't that be grand? Computers and the programs will start thinking and the people will stop.”

